quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  58,14,"Did you not see those who turn (in friendship) to people whom God's anger is upon them? They are not from you and (you are) not from them, and they swear falsely while they know"
  58,15,"God prepared a severe punishment for them, for what they were doing is indeed bad"
  58,16,"They took their oath as a shield to obstruct (people) from God's way, so they have a humiliating punishment"
  58,17,"Their possessions and children are of no use against God at all. They are inhabitants of the fire, remaining in there forever"
  58,18,"On a day that God raises them all, then they swear for Him as they swear for you, and they think that they are on to something. Know that indeed they are liars"
  58,19,"Satan overcame them and made them forget God's remembrance, they are Satan's party. Know that indeed Satan's party, they are the losers"
  58,20,"Indeed those who oppose God and His messenger, they are among the lowest ones"
  58,21,"God prescribed: I and My messengers shall be victorious. God is indeed strong and powerful"
  58,22,"You do not find any group who believe in God and the last day that they love those who oppose God and His messenger, even if they are their fathers or their sons or their brothers or their family (and tribe members). He wrote the belief in their hearts and He assisted them with a spirit from Him, and He admits them to gardens which rivers flow through them, remaining in there forever. God is pleased with them and they are pleased with Him, they are God's party. Know that God's party, they are indeed the successful ones"